      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-cyan-300/40 bg-slate-900/80 p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="space-y-2 max-w-xl">
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-200">Need Help Choosing the Right Project?</p>
          <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white">Speak with our advisory team for unbiased support</h2>
